boxmodell: 
block : margin, padding, height, width , border 
inline : margin, padding, border 
inline-block: margin, padding, height, width , border  också inline (ingen radbrytning)

span 
    display: inline-block;

--------------

Position: static, relative , absolute , fixed .     ( sticky ) 
  
    relative: 
          position:relative;
          left:30px;
          left, right , top, bottom  

          * behåller sin gammalt plats. 
    absolute: 
           position:absolute;
           left:30px;

 parents:  position:relative;
           
           * lämnar sin plats
           * parent element måste ha relative position


Flexbox: 
    För att ge one dimentional layout 

 


container /parent element > flex items

container -> 

display: flex , flex-direction, justify-content, align-items, align-content, flex-wrap


flex items: order, flex-shrink, flex-basis, flex, align-self





